headline: GTA Online
subtitle: GTA Online Bonuses: Premium Stunt Race (Sep 30 - Oct 3)
content: This weekend's Premium Stunt Race is a hot one. Beginning today, participate in the Bikes-locked ''Afterburner'' for Triple RP and a chance at hefty GTA$ payouts. To enter, head over to the yellow Premium Race Blip in Legion Square or join via the Quick Job App.
